main event: A brief observation of an unidentified light near Baltimore, Maryland.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on August 5, 1965, observers reported the object to be rapidly moving and disappearing., The object was described as showing rapid and erratic maneuvers at high altitude., The observation lasted for about 2 minutes with the object being approximately 500 ft. away., Officials concluded it was likely an aircraft influenced by unusual atmospheric conditions., This report is characteristic of many other UFO sightings reported in recent years.
witness description: the observer mentioned rapid and erratic maneuvers of the light
